'''Brendon Fraim''' is a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan who designed the [[Lyco Pibex]] in the [[Design An Alien]] contest held in the ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]s''. The entry was picked second place in the sixteen years and older category. He was twenty-two at the time his entry was published.<ref name="DAA">{{GalaxyCite|7|Design An Alien}}</ref>

